Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:21.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭！住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:22.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜賓教官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:25.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:27.35,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,帶著大家一起…
