Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:32.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是…要我們把你拋下嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你一個人不行的！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭！快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣下去你的戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:41.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哪怕我會…粉身碎骨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:43.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也要…！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:49.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:52.50,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:54.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Comment: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:56.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,向塔露拉 同時射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.60,0:02:34.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,掩護阿米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:47.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.07,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:57.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她們怎麼停止行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:02:58.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是戰術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,現在可不是拖拖拉拉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全員 按照指示進行撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.57,0:03:06.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:07.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:08.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,倒塌的 建築物廢墟中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:12.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有一處空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,從那裡穿過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只要離開廣場
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在出口的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:19.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就有個能藏身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們應該…怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:42.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}停下！別往霧裡面跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,只能死在這裡了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:52.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我不想死…我不想死…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:51.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:54.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請不要…從我身邊離開！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:03:59.90,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這範圍…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.16,0:04:02.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,已經就是極限了…
Comment: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:08.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,塔露拉大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:16.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:17.50,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的手！
