Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:23.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:23.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,高峰已經過了
