Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:29.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:32.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜賓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.08,0:05:37.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了解…
