Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:43.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:47.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你會和阿米婭…
