Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,保護好阿米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,拜託你了！
