Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續警戒周圍的環境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:20.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,臨光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:23.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,身為耀騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.88,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,無論是在什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.76,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都要成為指引人們的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:29.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:30.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:32.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:36.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,別讓他們的努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,全都白費！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.68,0:06:41.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.02,0:06:42.69,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:45.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace他們的情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都還好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:53.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,明白了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.33,0:07:04.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒關係的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:06.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace他們一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,會沒事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.59,0:07:09.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:11.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,羅德島的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都是很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:21.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:24.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼都已經這樣了還要戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真是無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,即使屍骨無存 也還這樣奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:31.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了不起的戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我會記住的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:35.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,羅德島
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:40.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我就知道想要順利的離開沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:48.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,搞好關係的第一步是自我介紹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:49.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你們可以稱呼我為W
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,W…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:55.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:57.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是不是在哪裡見過？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,W！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你有什麼目的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.56,0:08:04.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼目的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.52,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,能不能把博士交給我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:10.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.11,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,認識博士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,了如指掌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我可是專門為了見她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,才到這種地方來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,廢話少說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:21.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,別和她浪費時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.24,0:08:23.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:24.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你是叫阿米婭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我的事已經搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,後會有期！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:30.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,小兔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:31.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:33.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,再見！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:35.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:39.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她們就這麼撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:40.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:43.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但我總覺得 她們這幫人別有企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:52.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:54.32,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:55.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:56.95,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,隊長…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:08:59.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,其他的人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就只剩下你和我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:05.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:06.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,剛才除了慘叫什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,什麼都！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:14.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:21.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,別再說下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:23.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不然你的傷口會裂開的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:25.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我做了應急處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:27.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,再撐一會你就能走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.85,0:09:29.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你的左手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:33.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,至少還有一隻能用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:34.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:35.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:36.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你快逃吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,隊長一定可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:38.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:39.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.41,0:09:42.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,運輸機應該快趕到出口的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:44.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,被他們發現就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我去爭取點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:48.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:52.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Guard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.88,0:09:55.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你的命可是我廢了一隻手才換回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.47,0:10:01.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣我的手 也能創造些價值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:03.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:04.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:06.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,後會有期…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:08.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.19,0:10:16.19,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不爭氣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:36.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:40.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有種…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常悲傷的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:50.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Medic…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:54.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}請你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:56.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\an8}節哀順變…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.94,0:10:58.57,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有個人這麼對我說過…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:03.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,說在回到家前…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:05.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,要先把戰鬥後的眼淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好好藏起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.25,0:11:10.04,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們走吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:11.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:14.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回到羅德島…
Comment: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.24,0:11:43.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,看到那塊群生地帶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.95,0:11:46.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那些也是源石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就像你在廣場看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石就像隕石一樣 瘋狂地砸向地面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這就是天災
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.67,0:11:56.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在不同地域
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.96,0:11:59.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天災會以雪災或洪水等形式出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:02.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但它來臨的時候 一定會留下源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:04.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼大規模
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.59,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,會在地面上成長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:09.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,源石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,會成長？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然還不清楚具體情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是源石結晶的礦脈最終會破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:20.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,釋放出一種 叫作源石粒子的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:23.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,它們似乎會在空中匯聚成雲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:25.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,並且會引發新的天災
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.07,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,礦石病一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:30.33,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:33.37,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這和我們感染者的結局也非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:35.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天災
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,礦石病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還有人們的仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都在持續不斷地擴散著…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,杜賓！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:42.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你現在很累了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:44.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,最好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.22,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:48.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但你們不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,現在還是說說話 更輕鬆一些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:55.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:12:59.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你在這陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.69,0:13:02.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也受益匪淺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還能看到切爾諾伯格嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:09.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.62,0:13:13.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那個是在巨大的移動裝置上 所建造的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:17.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整座城市都是可以移動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,為了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,躲避天災嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:21.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:25.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,世界上絕大部分的城市都是可以移動的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,天災發生的地點 可以被預測到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.55,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以 通過提前移動城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.01,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就能預防天災
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:34.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.55,0:13:37.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,為什麼切爾諾伯格…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.35,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:41.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這一次的暴動…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可能有內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:48.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那些…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:50.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是去羅德島的人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:52.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,目的地是龍門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,龍門…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.95,0:13:58.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是要逃往更前方的城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,他們應該是從切爾諾伯格逃離的感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡是機長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.41,0:14:05.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,飛機馬上就要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.09,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:54.76,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:55.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我已經聽說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,任務…非常辛苦吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.89,0:15:02.44,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.15,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,臨光！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.61,0:15:05.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你沒事太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:06.52,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:08.48,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,抱歉 有誰能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.40,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,幫我把擔架準備一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:11.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我馬上拿過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:13.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們也來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:21.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她現在睡得很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,回到羅德島後…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整個人都放鬆下來了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她的經歷早就超過極限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:32.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:47.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您睡醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:50.82,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這一間是會客室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:56.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士閣下的房間 現在還正在準備中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.57,0:15:58.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以就先讓您在這裡休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:15:59.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.08,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們在羅德島的艦船中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您還可以選擇繼續休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:07.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:08.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,去外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:09.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就由我來帶您去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:12.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭女士那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:14.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,你很聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:15.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不及博士您的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:20.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,換洗的衣服 放置在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:23.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭女士目前正在甲板上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:26.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您從這邊走過去還有一定的距離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:28.69,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:30.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在過去的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:32.40,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我會順便向您介紹一下艦內的設備
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.86,0:16:33.74,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.66,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,羅德島艦船
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.91,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,當前正在朝著下一個目的地航行中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.00,0:16:49.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,請問您現在還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.55,0:16:53.84,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我真的什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:58.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,對於我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:00.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,和今後…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,帶路就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.64,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,羅德島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.94,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是一艘同時搭載了多種多樣的醫療設施的綜合陸行艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,除了手術所需的儀器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,以及藥劑處方之外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:22.87,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還備有專門用來研究礦石病的特殊設備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:26.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,運轉所需的能量全部由艦內提供
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.54,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這台機器會開採並提煉所需要的源石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.42,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們還會加工源石和其它貴金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.21,0:17:38.88,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,並與其他的城市和企業進行貿易上的往來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:41.30,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,居住區域
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.43,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是為了讓幹員和住院患者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.06,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,能夠舒適的生活而設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,由於執行任務和治療時
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:49.85,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所產生的精神上以及肉體上的負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:51.61,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,都能在這裡得到紓解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:53.99,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在羅德島
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:55.00,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不論種族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.70,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,出身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,是感染者還是非感染者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所有人都能夠愉快融洽地在一起生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:02.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,另外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.92,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,由於羅德島的活動範圍很廣泛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:07.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,因此 也會為大家提供運輸機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.80,0:18:09.89,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,各種武器和裝備等作為輔助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:14.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,閣下您已到達目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.68,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼介紹就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.48,0:18:18.10,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:19.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.19,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,她身上背負的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.19,0:18:27.11,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,很沉重…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:34.41,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,阿米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.58,0:18:37.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:40.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,您不去睡真的沒關係嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.71,0:18:44.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:45.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,現在很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.38,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一直睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.34,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,所以就跑來外面透透氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.97,0:18:55.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,塔露拉說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:57.56,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在腦海中揮之不去…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:00.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,確實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.15,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也許是個只會說空話的理想論者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:04.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:06.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還是想選擇正途
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:07.86,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,並為此付諸行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.03,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.86,0:19:13.16,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我所選擇的道路是否真的是正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我也曾深深的懷疑過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.20,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,而我的這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:20.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好像被她看穿了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:22.96,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.46,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這個時候對您說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.75,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,會讓您有負擔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:29.21,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:32.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace在通信中這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:34.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我會和你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.18,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,共同面對這個殘酷無情的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,這句話的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,真正的含義 我還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:49.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,如果堅持理想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:52.45,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,必然會和現實起衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:54.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.53,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,他仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.82,0:19:57.83,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,相信你會在正確的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.95,0:20:01.62,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,Ace…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.71,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,說的我都贊同…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:08.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我不可以再這樣迷茫下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.67,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:12.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,沒有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:15.51,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但我會一點點找回的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:17.39,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我一定會協助你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:21.60,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,實現理想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.89,0:20:23.98,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:24.81,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:25.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.23,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,請不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.27,0:20:29.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們在三天後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:31.49,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,還有新的任務需要去執行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.44,0:20:33.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:34.78,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,請博士好好休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:37.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,把自己恢復得精力充沛才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.16,0:20:39.79,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,那麼開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:50.63,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在切爾諾伯格的作戰中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.97,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們完成了 救出博士您的這一項任務
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然受了很大的損失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:20:59.72,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但是獲得了不少關於整合運動的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,在戰略上 可以說是成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.73,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,根據分析的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:06.31,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我們可以判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.36,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,整合運動的下一個攻擊目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:09.77,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就是炎國的龍門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:12.65,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,龍門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.61,0:21:15.28,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,雖然不像切爾諾伯格那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.82,0:21:18.24,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但龍門對待感染者也是非常苛刻的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.45,0:21:22.12,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,關於這一點 凱爾希醫生已經前往當地了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:25.29,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,與龍門代表的簽約工作也在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:27.17,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.42,0:21:29.25,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,羅德島就能在市內公開活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.13,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,但契約內容還沒定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.09,0:21:34.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,因此 希望博士和阿米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.47,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,可以前往龍門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:37.05,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,一起幫助凱爾希醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:38.80,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,簽訂和龍門之間的契約
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.47,0:21:40.26,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,簽約以後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:42.93,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,調查整合運動在龍門的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:44.14,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,就是你們的任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:45.27,ARZ-CHS,,0,0,0,,我了解了
